@max-wittig Wouldn't this be a bit dangerous since we do not have any kind of testing? We will be rebuild-pushing and not testing at all, the image could potentially not even launch and we'd not realize until we updated one of our hosts so pull is triggered. Or some other user opened an issue.

Currently we do not have testing either, but any time we pushed it was because we needed to make it work.

Why not use this opportunity to add it?

